I '''Maria Skłodowska-Curie''' ([[Noviembri 7]], [[1867]] - [[Juliu 4]], [[1934]]), metung yang [[w:physicist|physicist]] ampong [[w:chemist|chemist]] a [[w:Poland|Polaca]]-[[w:Francia|Francesa]] (''Polish-French''). Mibait yang Maria Skłodowska, dapot king [[w:France|Francia]] nung nu ya menuknangan king keraklan king bie na, kilala re king lagiung '''Marie Curie''' o '''Madame Curie'''. Mibait ya king Mibait ya king [[Warsaw]] king [[w:Poland|Polonia]] (Poland).   

Megi neng asawa i [[Pierre Curie]], a akayabe na murin king obra. Miayabe la ketang mumunang galal a Nobel (Nobel Prize) a simbut na. Dakal ya atuklasan a maki kaugnayan king [[radioactivity]]. Y aing mumunang taung sinambut aduang [[w:Nobel Prize|Galal a Nobel]], at ya pa murin ing sinambut kaniti para kareng mialiwang siensia. Ya ing mumunang babaing [[profesor]] king [[Sorbonne]].   

Pikabaluan ya uling ya ing mekatuklas king [[Radium]] ampong [[Polonium]], aduang [[w:chemical element|elementung]] radioactive, at dakal a abalu king kayang pamanigaral kareti. 

